{"tid":1656074,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"運動係時候進入 phase 2 培訓新人","createTime":"2019-10-15T11:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T06:05:50.000Z","uid":32906,"like":81,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"aa5895f54aeabd044ea1395dc357fb566457d4a8","tid":1656074,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:40:48.000Z","msg":"四個月以來，都係二百萬人既小部份人<br />\n支撐緊成個運動<br />\n身邊嘅人角色已經定晒位<br />\n勇武文宣來來去去都係同一班人<br />\n我身邊既勇武6月以黎無增加過<br />\n升級既又係同一班人<br />\n普通遊行集會派 已經跟唔上手足既升級<br />\n咁樣再耐d會出現斷層<br />\n勇武會被捕，文宣都會攰<br />\n所以林鄭同黑警覺得拉晒就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n我建議暫停再諗點升級<br />\n重點拉攏更多人參與<br />\n<br />\n勇武<br />\n重新組織一下 四個月黎既經驗<br />\n以老兵教新兵方式（記得耐心d 唔好日屌夜屌）<br />\ne.g.宣傳black block 概念<br />\n裝備選購教學<br />\n入場離場換裝<br />\n上到前線帶領新手<br />\n暫時減少被捕人士 增加新手嘅信心<br />\n你諗下我哋次次都俾人咁樣拉係人都驚左上前線<br />\n我仲提議<br />\n和平集會時可以做下black block 教育想去前線既新手<br />\n開一個區練投擲 健身區 練跑區之類做下訓練<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣<br />\n可以重推派memo紙比人寫呢個活動<br />\n帶野比人貼下<br />\n開poster 集中 post 方便佢地印野出去貼<br />\n增加遊行人士參與度<br />\n鼓勵佢哋加入幫手做文宣<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩新諗法都可以講 <br />\n重點係推動更多人行多一步"},{"pid":"4efa51f278487d0f307f7cf3d4e957dc7b3954a3","tid":1656074,"uid":32906,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"係時候回歸番和平遊行<br />\n政府唔回應<br />\n鼓勵升級<br />\n用呢 個loop 集結更多行多一步既人"},{"pid":"156e177f5b0cfa01a8f905efc18b08ab7f1616c3","tid":1656074,"uid":249263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"仲有記得twitter戰線<br />\n<br />\n一人拉身邊一個人開twitter acc<br />\n<br />\n200萬人不是夢<br />\n（而家得4000人retweet 咋屌）<br />\n<br />\n用下twitter help 去每日領任務retweet<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=50bbacf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbot的作用幫大家響twitter大海中<br />\n搵一啲重要的tweets<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">task2 係議員外媒tweets大家去retweet la</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n只要輸入 /task2 就可以知道外國議員外媒名人出左咩重要tweet，大家去retweet啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8KyGMc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8KyGMc.png&h=aeb55a2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cdc93b48f8908ccd075fcef0012c6d7e7b77067","tid":1656074,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"我角度黎睇蒙面法前一晚已經係end game<br />\n當晚勇武曬馬，怒氣上到最高點<br />\n以現時黎睇好難再勁得過當晚<br />\n咁不如暫緩下 招多d人<br />\n準備黎多次咁上下規模既示威"},{"pid":"304e8d797ca6f439c59ba96525db3e4728fd1730","tid":1656074,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773d11e63b16e3a2bd5bf1696f189695a098f10e","tid":1656074,"uid":70403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"有冇喺集會個時演習下防暴捉手足？<br />\n加強應變能力"},{"pid":"ba7324444882da3f805097a20cb1afd8763854ae","tid":1656074,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"773d11e63b16e3a2bd5bf1696f189695a098f10e","tid":1656074,"uid":70403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"有冇喺集會個時演習下防暴捉手足？<br />\n加強應變能力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"okay喎 帶齊裝對抗下"},{"pid":"50a17c57a693e0f82606ad9f22e4374df7a7f37b","tid":1656074,"uid":32906,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"773d11e63b16e3a2bd5bf1696f189695a098f10e","tid":1656074,"uid":70403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"有冇喺集會個時演習下防暴捉手足？<br />\n加強應變能力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"暴大都好似搞過類似既活動<br />\n廣場練武"},{"pid":"2eec9832dcf974c111d3fcd52fe5c4f4b7301050","tid":1656074,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T1